# 🛡️ Titan Sentinel

### Real-Time System Monitoring & Alert Engine

Titan Sentinel is a lightweight, real-time system monitoring tool designed to track CPU, RAM, and Disk usage, generate performance reports, and trigger alerts based on configurable thresholds.

Built with Python and designed to run in headless Linux environments, this project demonstrates practical system monitoring, logging, and alerting concepts commonly used in production environments.

## Features

* Real-time monitoring of:
  * CPU usage
  * RAM usage
  * Disk usage
* Configurable alert thresholds
* Telegram alert integration
* Automatic performance report generation (PNG)
* Logging system (CSV format)
* Graceful shutdown with report generation

## Tech Stack

* Python 3
* psutil
* matplotlib
* requests

