## ⚙️ Installation

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/titan-sentinel.git
cd titan-sentinel

Install dependencies:

pip install psutil matplotlib requests


---

## Usage

Run the monitor:

```
python sentinel.py
```

Stop execution safely:

```
Ctrl + C
```

Upon shutdown, the system will automatically:

* Generate a performance graph
* Save logs to CSV

---

## Output

* `system_report.png` → Visual performance graph
* `system_log.csv` → Raw metrics data

---

## Alerts (Optional)

Configure:

* `telegram_token.txt`
* `telegram_id.txt`

The system will send alerts when thresholds are exceeded.

